title: Grant Morrison - DC work in rough reading order + Vertigo stuff.
description:
A complete digital rips repack of Grant Morrison's DC/Vertigo work.

I've organised everything in a rough reading order.

This includes: JLA, Batman, The Flash, 52, Seven Soldiers of Victory, Final Crisis, Batman and Robin, Batman Incorporated, Batman - Legends of the Dark Knight, The Return of Bruce Wayne, Batman - The Return, Action Comics, The Multiversity, All Star Superman, Animal Man, Doom Patrol, Flex Mentallo, The Filth, The Invisibles, Seaguy, Vimanarama, WE3 and Joe the Barbarian.

All credit to the original rippers
